     C                   move      COV01u        wscvp1
     C     KUKEY         KLIST
     C                   KFLD                    FIFIRM
     C                   KFLD                    KUNDNR
     C     AWBKEY        KLIST
     C                   KFLD                    dfuni             1
     C                   KFLD                    wsavd
